  </div>

  <div id='footer-open'>^</div>

  <div id='about-box'>
    <div id='close-about-box'>x</div>
    <h1>3gtv</h1>


    <p><strong>Controls:</strong>
      <ul><li>Space: skip</li>
      <li>M: pause/open menu</li>
      <li>Scrollwheel: zoom</li></ul></p>

    <div id='trends-chart'>
      <img src='./assets/img/trendschart.png' /><br>
      <a href='http://www.google.co.uk/trends/explore?hl=en-US#q=.3gp&cmpt=q&tz=Etc/GMT&tz=Etc/GMT'>View full Google Trends report</a>.
    </div>

    <p>
    '3gp' is a largely extinct file container that was most popular during the first wave of video-playing mobile phones - the days of RAZRs and Nokia N70s.<br><br>
    3GTV is a randomized viewing platform for the one million or so .3gp files that have found their way onto Youtube.<br>
    </p>

